                            <comment id="13663" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Sun, 26 Jun 2005 06:01:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for spotting this! It seems that the correct solution is to use a Set there: each bean name should only be contained once, after all. I&apos;ve fixed this accordingly; will make it into today&apos;s 1.2.2 release!&lt;/p&gt;

